>> title: Martinez
>> tags: gin,old-tom-gin,tumbler,shaken

Chill a #cocktail glass{} in the freezer.

Fill a #cocktail shaker{} with @ice{}.

Add @Luxardo Maraschino liqueur{1/4%oz}, @Carpano antica red vermouth{3/4%oz}, @Dolin dry white vermouth{3/4%oz}, and @Old Tom gin{2%oz} to shaker.

Shake vigrously for at 30-45 seconds.

Strain with #Hawthorne strainer{} into glass. Serve with a @maraschino cherry{1}.